<C>__{interior fourth grade day}
<A>__{salvatore is sitting at the front row desk next to peppino, a little freckle faced boy. his attention, like that of the whole class, is concentrated on what is taking place at the blackboard. the teacher is standing there, watching a plump little boy, shy and not quite all there, do a two figure multiplication it is nicola scorsone, known as 'cola'. he is red in the face, has one purple ear and one white one. he stares in terror at that '255 x 15' written on the blackboard. the teacher yells, waving a birch rod in her hand.}
<C>__{teacher}
<D>__{well then?! five times five equals...?}
<A>__{cola stops to think a moment, then...}
<C>__{cola}
<D>__{thirty!}
<A>__{the teacher grabs him by the purple ear and bashes his head against the numbers on the blackboard. a large thud echoes through the room, followed by a roar of laughter. the teacher slams her rod on the desk.}
<C>__{teacher}
<D>__{silence!!}
